column3: At last... The power to reclaim what is mine. What is <Emphasis>ours</Emphasis>...

The will of Queen Gunnhildr shall not be denied.
All who oppose Bozja must fall.
By the gods... She has become a vessel for the blade's power!

No... No, we have suffered too long for it to end this way.
Bozja is <Emphasis>ours</Emphasis>! If we cannot have it, no one will!
